<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

<p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> July 14, 2026</p>

<p>
StockWise ("we", "our", or "us") respects your privacy.
This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information while using the StockWise application.
</p>

<h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>

<ul>
<li>Business Information</li>
<li>Product Information</li>
<li>Inventory Data</li>
<li>Sales Records</li>
<li>Customer Information</li>
<li>Device Information</li>
<li>Crash Reports</li>
<li>Analytics Data</li>
</ul>

<h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>

<ul>
<li>Manage inventory</li>
<li>Track sales</li>
<li>Generate reports</li>
<li>Create invoices</li>
<li>Improve app performance</li>
<li>Provide customer support</li>
</ul>

<h2>3. Advertisements</h2>

<p>
The free version of StockWise may display advertisements using Google AdMob.
Google may collect certain device information to provide relevant advertisements.
</p>

<h2>4. In-App Purchases</h2>

<p>
Premium subscriptions and one-time purchases are securely processed by Google Play Billing.
We never store your payment information.
</p>

<h2>5. Cloud Backup</h2>

<p>
If you enable cloud backup, your business data may be securely stored using Firebase Cloud Storage or related Google services.
</p>

<h2>6. Data Security</h2>

<p>
We use reasonable security measures to protect your data from unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction.
</p>

<h2>7. Data Sharing</h2>

<p>
We do not sell or rent your personal information.
Information may be shared only with trusted services required for app functionality such as:
</p>

<ul>
<li>Google Firebase</li>
<li>Google AdMob</li>
<li>Google Play Billing</li>
</ul>

<h2>8. Your Rights</h2>

<ul>
<li>Access your data</li>
<li>Update your information</li>
<li>Delete your account (if applicable)</li>
<li>Disable cloud backup</li>
</ul>

<h2>9. Children's Privacy</h2>

<p>
StockWise is not intended for children under the age of 13.
We do not knowingly collect personal information from children.
